      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>it's just a story though, you know? i'm talking about the character. the character is just a bunch of code that's being wiped away. it feels so much more real than real life sometimes. like, why fight to keep something alive when the system has already decided it's obsolete? it's just easier to let the code go. don't you think there's a certain kind of beauty in just... letting it all be erased?",
